* VERSION 1.4
  - Moved project source code to a Eclipse-like structure (as seen in current Oracle examples).
  - Changed build process and project structure to allow usage on SQLDev v18 and newer.
  - Changed PreparedStatement and Connection handling across thread executions to avoid leaks
  - Moved Strings on Java classes to constants
  - Moved Logger to a helper class to allow usage across extension.

-- Fork --

* VERSION 1.3
  - Merged fix on open cursors from Github user jdiazest's fork
  - Extension icon changed
  - Added script for building the extension ZIP

* VERSION 1.2
  - The logging is no longer interfering with user input
  - Solved other minor issues (please refer to the issue tracker on Github)
  - Merged new input dialog from Github user eftewuer's fork
